        <h2>Oil Painting</h2>
        <p>
          Albrecht Dürer painted a vast number of oil paintings, including religious scenes,
          portraits and landscapes.
        </p>
        <img src="/imgs/Albrecht_Dürer-Adam_and_Eve_(Prado).jpg" alt="Painting of Adam and Eve" />
        <figcaption><em>Adam and Eve</em>, 1507, Museo del Prado</figcaption>
      </div>
      <div class="medium-card">
        <h2 class="left">Drawings</h2>
        <img
          src="/imgs/Self-portrait_at_13_by_Albrecht_Dürer.jpg"
