      <div class="medium-card">
        <h2>Engravings</h2>
        <p>
          Engravings both in metal and woodcuts were one of the artist's favourite techniques in his
          later years.
        </p>
        <img
          src="/imgs/Albrecht_Dürer_-_Melencolia_I_.jpg"
          alt="Engraving of a melancholic angel"
        />
        <figcaption><em>Melancolia I</em>, 1514</figcaption>
      </div>
      <div class="medium-card">
        <h2 class="left">Watercolours</h2>
        <img src="/imgs/Albrecht_Dürer_-_Hare_1502.jpg" alt="Watercolour of a hare" />
        <figcaption><em>Young Hare</em>, 1502</figcaption>
